  "body": "### Component\n\nAnvil\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nCreateX already deployed on 56 chains: https://github.com/pcaversaccio/createx\r\n\r\nIncludes Create3 factory. \r\n\r\nProposal - handle in the similar manner like Nick's contract is handled. \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/pull/5391\r\n\r\ni.e. Include the CreateX factory deployer when starting up anvil by default, and add a new --disable-default-createx-deployer flag to not deploy it. It will also not be deployed if anvil is forking, to properly simulate the conditions of that chain.\r\n\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
